Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the control flow in the eProsima Integration Service:

```plantuml
@startuml eProsima_Integration-Service

participant "Configuration Parser" as CP
participant "Integration Service Core" as ISC
participant "System Handle Factory" as SHF
participant "System Handle A" as SHA
participant "System Handle B" as SHB
participant "Data Converter" as DC

activate CP
CP -> ISC : Parse YAML configuration
activate ISC

ISC -> SHF : Create System Handles
activate SHF
SHF --> ISC : Return System Handles
deactivate SHF

ISC -> SHA : Initialize
activate SHA
SHA --> ISC : Initialization complete
deactivate SHA

ISC -> SHB : Initialize
activate SHB
SHB --> ISC : Initialization complete
deactivate SHB

ISC -> ISC : Set up routes

loop For each message
    SHA -> ISC : Receive message
    ISC -> DC : Convert message (JSON to xtypes)
    activate DC
    DC --> ISC : Converted message
    deactivate DC
    ISC -> SHB : Forward converted message
end

@enduml
```